    <name>X-Plorist</name>
    <description>Tourist guide that displays all the important monuments, pubs, shops in a given area and offers a possibility of adding new places and reviewing the existing ones. It will be done in Ionic framework with Cordova in the background, as a hybrid mobile application for iOS, Android and Windows platforms.</description>
